children.text: How to use: Photo Cube Lite must first be set as your home screen wallpaper. Click here to select Photo Cube Lite from your list of wallpapers.
This free version has limited functionality, click here to buy the full version to gain access to the full range of settings, backgrounds, frames, effects, saved cubes and more!
Set pictures to be shown on the cube
Set colour and picture for background
Set the number of floating panels in the background
Set size and position of cube
